publisher			Philip Day							
publish_time	 2016年4月4日		
desc_long								关于这款软件							Whirligig is an immersive film player / publisher. That is to say it is designed to playback fisheye, fisheye stereo SBS, 360 fisheye, 360 fisheye stereo SBS, barrel panoramic, barrel panoramic stereo SBS, 16x9, 16x9 stereo SBS, 16x9 Curved and 16x9 curved Stereo SBS.Video Format SupportWhirligig supports direct show filters and standard operating system formats. In practice what this means is that without installing any codecs you can play back avi's and if you install the related codecs you can play back those video formats.Important Notice.Without the codecs correctly installed you will find only a small amount of files can be played back. I have written a guide in the dissusion board to help get the codecs installed and working for Whirligig.http://steamcommunity.com/app/451650/discussions/0/364042262873027118/Image SupportCurrent image support is limited to png's and jpg's. It is highly recommend that the images you view are of a resolution of a factor of two.						
